{"tid":2412278,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彩雲邨男入老麥拒掃「安心出行」 打傷職員走甩埋","createTime":"2021-02-18T02:42:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T06:20:07.000Z","uid":239336,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e786869eba094a3423a419dd7c475e9038e2fcf4","tid":2412278,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:42:32.000Z","msg":"政府早前宣佈今日起恢復晚市堂食，每枱人數可增至四人，但「交換條件」是食客必須掃描「安心出行」二維碼或登記姓名、電話、到訪日期和時間。員工須每14天檢測，違規食肆負責人要負刑責。但新規定實施首日，黃大仙有食肆疑因此發生襲擊案。<br />\n<br />\n清晨6時許，一名40多歲男子走入彩雲邨商場麥當勞，職員要求他掃描「安心出行」二維碼或留下個人資料被拒，該男子更情緒激動，出手襲擊20多歲男職員，他前額受輕傷，由接報救護員送院。案件列作襲擊，警方正翻看閉路電視追緝該名涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210218/UEJWD6V365EU3DDADUXM3GM4DM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210218%2FUEJWD6V365EU3DDADUXM3GM4DM%2F&d=3nH4Hj8OzEJ%2Fsn4LiTBSOobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=3f673af2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210218%2FUEJWD6V365EU3DDADUXM3GM4DM%2F&h=6fb2a087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210218/UEJWD6V365EU3DDADUXM3GM4DM/</a>"},{"pid":"d6b530455732fa92b9b8f117ea52370716a7104a","tid":2412278,"uid":191815,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"打份工啫<br />\n隻眼開隻眼閉咪算囉<br />\n係要正義之師上身<br />\n睇個款十足十做老麥以為自己當差嘅藍血人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a2af20f86c288f218569d335babc8532501f78","tid":2412278,"uid":71433,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d6b530455732fa92b9b8f117ea52370716a7104a","tid":2412278,"uid":191815,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:45:26.000Z","msg":"打份工啫<br />\n隻眼開隻眼閉咪算囉<br />\n係要正義之師上身<br />\n睇個款十足十做老麥以為自己當差嘅藍血人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"明顯做藍店個腦都有問題啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\"